HEADWORD: Appellatory
<hw>Ap*pel"la*tory</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>appellatorius</ets>, fr. <ets>appellare</ets>.]</ety>
<def>Containing an appeal.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>An <qex>appellatory</qex> libel ought to contain the name of the
